OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnions row threatens fight 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor 3,000 steel jobs       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Infighting by unions is jeopardising   
OL,6, attempts to save thousands of steel    
OL,7, making jobs, the BBC has been told.    
OL,9,FThe UK's largest steel plant at Port   
OL,10,FTalbot is facing 3,000 job cuts under  
OL,11,Fplans being considered by owner Tata.  
OL,13,FThere is a deep rift with Community and
OL,14,FGMB on one side and Unite on the other,
OL,15,Fwhich has withdrawn its support for a  
OL,16,Fcross-union approach to talks.         
OL,18,FIt is understood Community, the largest
OL,19,Fsteel union, has invited Unite leaders 
OL,20,Fto meet next week to resolve divisions.
